             was indicted for <rs id="t18160214-4-off17" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18160214-4-off17" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160214-4-off17" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18160214-4-cd18" type="crimeDate">10th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160214-4-off17 t18160214-4-cd18"></join>, one silver milk pail, value 24s. one silver milk ewer, value 15s. and one silver spoon, value 5s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18160214-4-victim91" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           St. Poyyer
                        <interp inst="t18160214-4-victim91" type="surname" value="St. Poyyer"></interp>
